t-align:center;\" |135\n|-\n!scope=row|US ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' [[Billboard Hot 100|Hot 100]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://new.music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart_watch/74423/week-ending-oct-9-2011-songs-someone-like-adele/;_ylt=AmzJa4yFQId9Uyr6aBsCy08PwiUv |title=Week Ending Oct. 9, 2011. Songs: Someone Like Adele |last=Grein |first=Paul |work=Yahoo! |publisher=new.music.yahoo.com |date=12 October 2011 |accessdate=13 October 2011}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|74\n|-\n!scope=row|US [[Hot Dance Club Songs]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref name=\"chartbeat\" />\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\n|-\n!scope=row|US [[Mainstream Top 40 (Pop Songs)|Pop Songs]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref name=\"chartbeat\" />\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|39\n|-\n!scope=row|US [[Latin Pop Songs]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/#/column/chartbeat/chart-highlights-band-perry-s-young-tops-1005457832.story|title=Chart Highlights: Band Perry's 'Young' Tops Adult Contemporary|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=31 October 2011|accessdate=31 October 2011}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|31\n|}\n\n=== Certifications ===\n{{certification Table Top}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=single|region=Australia|artist=Enrique Iglesias|title=I Like How It Feels|award=Gold|certyear=2011|relyear=2011|access-date=11 June 2012|digital=true}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=single|region=Canada|artist=Enrique Iglesias|title=I Like How It Feels|award=Platinum|certyear=2012|relyear=2011|access-date=11 June 2012|digital=true}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=single|region=Mexico|artist=Enrique Iglesias|title=I Like How It Feels|award=Platinum|certyear=2014|relyear=2011|access-date=30 May 2014|digital=true}}\n{{certification Table Bottom}}\n\n== Release history ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n!scope=\"col\"|Country\n!scope=\"col\"|Date\n!scope=\"col\"|Format\n!scope=\"co